title NIN Verification Bypass
actor Customer
actor Admin
actor Agent
participant Biosmart
participant CLM
participant EDA

Customer->Agent:Request for Sim Registration 


Admin->Biosmart : Login as Administrator
Admin->Biosmart: Update Settings to allow NIN Verification Bypass
Admin->Biosmart : Activate NIN Bypass feature
Biosmart-->Biosmart: Persist \nNIN Bypass \nconfiguration



Agent->Biosmart:Launch Biosmart
Agent->Biosmart:Login with Credentials
Agent->Biosmart:Select SIM registration Menu

Biosmart-->Biosmart: Add NIN Bypass as \n a Verification Type
Biosmart-->Biosmart: Display only Nigeria \n as Country option
Biosmart-->Agent: Display SIM Registration Form \nwith Enrollment Type options

opt Register with NIN

Customer->Agent: Provides NIN details 

Agent->Biosmart: Verify NIN of Customer
Biosmart-->Agent: Returns Customer Details 
Biosmart-->Agent: Enter State, LGA 
Agent->Biosmart: Submit
end

opt Register with NIN Bypass

Agent->Biosmart: Select NIN Verification Bypass

Biosmart-->Biosmart: Returns customer Details 
Agent->Biosmart: Submit
end

Biosmart->CLM: Submit Customer information
CLM-->CLM: Calculate Barring or Expiry Date

